{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b6aa98ffa","title":"中央文革小组办事组、全军文革小组办公室关于《新疆日报》社事件的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f7cff9ef88","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"}],"tags":[{"id":"268718f23b","name":"新闻广播和出版","type":"主题"},{"id":"32c17dd6c3","name":"中央文革、全军文革小组联合文件","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cbc046a9a6","type":"title","text":"中央文革小组办事组、全军文革小组办公室关于《新疆日报》社事件的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"6c264a45fb","type":"paragraph","text":"新疆军区党委、红二司、革命职工联合总部，并抄有关各群众组织：（均请新疆军区抄转）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"b3c9932fd3","type":"paragraph","text":"一、要坚决贯彻毛主席关于“要文斗，不要武斗”的指示，参加武斗的双方，要立即停止武斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"0cf0ff8e54","type":"paragraph","text":"二、新疆日报社为军管单位，各群众组织都不要去冲，也不要查封，进入报社的外单位群众组织，要立即退出报社。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"001d142c32","type":"paragraph","text":"三、新疆日报的问题，由新疆军区组织双方代表通过协商解决。报纸出版如有缺点错误，可以提出批评。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"ddcac80f02","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组办事组","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"25e45c5720","type":"paragraph","text":"全军文革小组办公室","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"},{"id":"92e491ca9c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年五月八日二十三时","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa"}],"page":{"id":"026c578671","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8b6aa98ffa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}